701917f-a.title: Bronx: Trinity Avenue - 158th Street (East)
701917f-a.text:
(1)
Trinity Ave., at the N.E. corner of East 158th Street, showing, under construction, P.S. No. 51. This is a rear view of the school
as seen from Jackson Ave.
1915.
Gift of Samuel Landsm.an
(2)
The same, from the opposite direction, as seen across East
158th Street, near Jackson Ave.
1915.
Gift of Samuel Landsan
